  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to Improve local house structures in Jorgue, Les Irois</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The repair/rehabilitation of houses damaged by the storm will ensure long term positive change for communities and ensure they are more resilient to future disasters. The cash grants will also see significant change in the long term prospect for families and communities in rebuilding their livelihoods in a sustainable way</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will work with 116 families affected by the passage of Matthew to rehabilitate and repair damaged homes. A further 100 families who have lost fishing equipment, crops and reserves of seeds and food will be supported through direct cash grants.</narrative>
  </description>
